{"tid":2331602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！","createTime":"2020-12-19T02:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T08:47:09.000Z","uid":2720,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22b8b94024c530e6da3e3f4ff17da251d9122681","tid":2331602,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母<br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20121218/Q5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2FQ5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=12d270d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2FQ5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA%2F&h=1b25dbf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20121218/Q5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA/</a>"},{"pid":"b558f69c0433eb2e7299db1789dc0ff68b99f80d","tid":2331602,"uid":151074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:12:21.000Z","msg":"條友嘅童年都好撚柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a42b957a66965160d4a5a5cf83a925e2bbfaaed","tid":2331602,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"施永青 聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cf70ee03cc